teesri &lt;unk&gt; : the hidden camera ( hindi : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; : the hidden camera ) is a 2006 indian political action thriller film directed by harry baweja . the film stars sunny deol , sunil shetty , raveena tandon and naseeruddin shah in the lead roles . the film 's music is composed by pritam . the film is a remake of the 2006 hindi film of the same name .